{"tid":1297532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(檢討post)亂咁玩膠散佈謠言，會有三個後果","createTime":"2019-07-08T15:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T19:22:29.000Z","uid":146454,"like":168,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c702f0ce39580ae3c57c8e7ab783ccddc1875bf6","tid":1297532,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:58:32.000Z","msg":"第一個後果係會令資訊混亂，啲人開始質疑呢度嘅資訊。以後出咩事呢度嘅巴絲只會先判斷咗究竟傳遞嘅訊息係咪真定假，直接影響咗遊擊嘅成效。<br />\n<br />\n第二連登仔自己圍内互片。或者可能一開頭得一兩個post係玩野，但係如果有人有心玩嘢同分化，佢只需要出多幾個post贈興，挑起對罵，已經可以令內部分化，唔使靠共產黨自己已經瓦解。<br />\n<br />\n最後一樣嘢係，真係有人借機行事。呢一刻真係好驚有絕望嘅真心膠今晚做咗傻事。<br />\n<br />\n點都好，今晚行為真係要檢討，不篤灰不割蓆。"},{"pid":"4276ec00997f80915fea7b0add3cfb800ad12df0","tid":1297532,"uid":146454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:59:03.000Z","msg":"玩膠，真係一次就夠啦"},{"pid":"38b28e1904d836580546c36e30bd09db90e5c3e5","tid":1297532,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec59a09e889ff992843d1411db573eb87832ca37","tid":1297532,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:00:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bdff80271dd323509d3aa59ede3805fcb678df3c","tid":1297532,"uid":111899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:00:19.000Z","msg":"挺"},{"pid":"b3879832f08363f9cb232e0f592feab6d3f218e6","tid":1297532,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:01:09.000Z","msg":"推，玩還玩，玩得高章d"},{"pid":"7eda3d3e7368df992958d430605044e906bf6bbd","tid":1297532,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:02:04.000Z","msg":"依家有夠民氣，應該搞多次百萬人上街<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dgazeS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dgazeS</a>"},{"pid":"9be8b7ef26358fd63b30848f3352eed06481772f","tid":1297532,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:03:09.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":