"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食完屎先好翻黎揾我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />💩💩💩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c604b4aced7d71058a221b9178e7245b8b3e9323","tid":1297532,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dde892e917a3e856e51395a88f2fe234b2066028","tid":1297532,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:57:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">［抗分化］共匪宜家玩緊老技倆，拉籠一派打一派</span></span><br />\n<br />\n共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，政府有時會軟硬兼施，打下感情牌博同情，亦會派五毛做打手，屌/笑/鬧/玩膠嗰啲當然90%都係三毛，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，所謂拉籠一派打一派，群眾鬥群眾就係咁，要你自相殘殺，孤立主要敵人，民初時期國民政府分裂就係共匪搞出嚟<br />\n<br />\n共匪玩咗咁多年分化，普羅大眾應該要熟悉呢一點，大家都係擁抱自由民主嘅價值，呢個要保持頭腦清晰，和理非同勇武都係一齊合作嘅同伴，同伴之間要互相尊重，唔好咁易中咗政府同三毛嘅分化計<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今次唔排除有三毛混入開假膠post / 推膠post，之前嗰啲垃圾post我當一時on9，如果今日起（9/7/2019）再發現有任何人開膠post，一律當三毛處理</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:28:04.000Z","msg":"其實真係最驚啲人搞分化<br />\n連登最重要嘢係自由，呢一樣嘢亦都係對家會利用嘅武器。<br />\n所以我哋係要鍛鍊自己個思維，提防有人喺我哋入面扮自己人製造仇恨。<br />\n<br />\n不過我又覺得唔使用重典嘅，<br />\n始終香港人經歷咗咁多都攰，連登仔更加攰<br />\n畀佢哋玩膠抒發下情緒都好。<br />\n好似分化藍絲，就係一個好好嘅例子，玩之餘不失分寸<br />\n只不過唔好太離譜就得，我覺得今次呢件事最好嘅教訓就係，任何嘅策略都唔可以對戰友造成傷害，呢一條會係玩膠嘅底線。"},{"pid":"43feadefd913cdc1ec546413c5a8dcd9d37429bb","tid":1297532,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc3ee004024f0db58a649d6fb05d66cbe69df5c5","tid":1297532,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:58:27.000Z","msg":"小心三毛帶風向"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:31:30.000Z","msg":"其實你知道三毛會做啲乜嘢，反而冇咁驚。<br />\n我覺得唔駛攻擊自己人，檢討完就得，<br />\n始終戰友，做錯事都依然係戰友。<br />\n<br />\n所以而家最重要嘅係諗下發生咩事，保持冷靜息事寧人，諗下教訓，訓覺close file"},{"pid":"c91cdf5a81d87e01a305285ba59f22e21adbc64e","tid":1297532,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc3ee004024f0db58a649d6fb05d66cbe69df5c5","tid":1297532,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:58:27.000Z","msg":"小心三毛帶風向"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:32:57.000Z","msg":"所以某程度上今日發生呢種爭論係一個好事， 連登仔係要針對外來網嘅分化，做好多演習"},{"pid":"a1d920f70baefbc9a28527385bcb1abcfb0d82a2","tid":1297532,"uid":146454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"78b9e3d3a384bbfbdc7510a2b6bde909bee8a3d9","tid":1297532,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"591d9378adc813f9d4831411ffdfe8b34649fd78","tid":1297532,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d849ef4546c86d8c809aa847e35206d75ed6a294","tid":1297532,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fe56f57f1d74ee6d949b2ba671018e66e43677","tid":1297532,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1d920f70baefbc9a28527385bcb1abcfb0d82a2","tid":1297532,"uid":146454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"78b9e3d3a384bbfbdc7510a2b6bde909bee8a3d9","tid":1297532,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"591d9378adc813f9d4831411ffdfe8b34649fd78","tid":1297532,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:53:56.000Z","msg":"講講下諗起呢篇文<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1271219/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1271219/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我最驚呢度啲人覺得連登係大台，淨係靠呢一度唔肯諗，或者就覺得贏咗網絡就贏咗支持。 咁樣只會重蹈雨革覆轍。<br />\n<br />\n更加驚嘅係民意會因為政府換人或撤回方案就熱情冷卻，覺得自己贏咗。"},{"pid":"ce08d9c4043b14aa8a508579ec00bb3ec6493de9","tid":1297532,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:55:27.000Z","msg":"問題已經唔係一條條例，一個政府官員，<br />\n亦都唔只係政府濫權。<br />\n<br />\n咁多日之後希望有人發覺問題出自制度不公。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55362cbed627a08161ff899e79ecf55a809bebda","tid":1297532,"uid":105578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:01:51.000Z","msg":"玩還玩，唔該知錯快快手開post道歉，唔好見到俾人圍插先黎道歉，今次係極幼稚既行為，唔好覺得睇唔明既係人地問題, blame the victims 只會係火上加油"},{"pid":"3bc2e1335c28227bd6a26cadc35a5f7bad09daaf","tid":1297532,"uid":105578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:03:54.000Z","msg":"冇出到去根本唔明出左去既有幾失望，係依個時候仲出膠post，根本弱智"},{"pid":"b25c2d882f81c22ef076120148041832718c1bb7","tid":1297532,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5880fa5ef510f7f91f74bf9a86f8efe50a5a4ec2","tid":1297532,"uid":146454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"88c7a38902aa0bb610ce13edd50dd4359788e522","tid":1297532,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:08:09.000Z","msg":"我覺得應該集中一個po 去做呢樣野"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:47:12.000Z","msg":"我諗連開膠post嘅人都估唔到成件事會咁演變成咁<br />\n好可能佢哋以為兩個post就完<br />\n但係點知其他人越開越多， 然之後有啲自己人不明所以信以為真。 <br />\n之所以失控，因為冇人可以控制到其他人做任何行為。呢個係將來連登要面對嘅漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n真係好多人信㗎。頭先打緊文宣執緊被捕須知，忽然女朋友驚到死打黎叫我如果去金鐘千祈要好好保護自己，唔好死咗去。我心諗做乜事。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:04:27.000Z","msg":"開頭都以為玩膠<br />\n但突然啲Post多到洗版咁多<br />\n真心以為有咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e873b447ef0d09cbc50e01d18313c00ae1a981","tid":1297532,"uid":33292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4276ec00997f80915fea7b0add3cfb800ad12df0","tid":1297532,"uid":146454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:59:03.000Z","msg":"玩膠，真係一次就夠啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:07:06.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 一次都嫌多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f9067b9dd9a895bcc0878014174c27ee7344e9","tid":1297532,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bc2e1335c28227bd6a26cadc35a5f7bad09daaf","tid":1297532,"uid":105578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:03:54.000Z","msg":"冇出到去根本唔明出左去既有幾失望，係依個時候仲出膠post，根本弱智"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"成晚都忙緊冇睇post 一見到通知 <br />\n都即刻準備出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n越睇越唔對路先知道原來成班人喺度玩<br />\n<br />\n最慘應該係嗰一班冇帳號，但係走咗去金鐘最後食白果嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06ad30a3e9cf3708be585012f09be5bcae5d0c2","tid":1297532,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31e873b447ef0d09cbc50e01d18313c00ae1a981","tid":1297532,"uid":33292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4276ec00997f80915fea7b0add3cfb800ad12df0","tid":1297532,"uid":146454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:59:03.000Z","msg":"玩膠，真係一次就夠啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:07:06.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 一次都嫌多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:14:35.000Z","msg":"其實我係刻意冇講道德問題<br />\n之所以唔支持咁樣嬉皮笑臉，係因為義士死咗，我覺得要尊重佢哋。<br />\n但係我都明白太過壓抑未必係好事，所以玩膠係可以理解，只不過佢哋今次明顯錯判。<br />\n<br />\n反正仆左，仆一次就好。而家要做嘅嘢係避免傷口擴大"}]}